Help Type: topic
Topic: command

Command Overview

Object commands:
  wikigraph <object-uri>
  wikigraph <scope-uri>
  wikigraph <scope-uri> --query <query>
  wikigraph <chunk-uri|entity-uri> related
  wikigraph <entity|triple|summary|chunk-uri> evidence
  wikigraph next <cursor>
  wikigraph <located-chunk-uri|located-entity-uri> pack

URI routing:
  URI-addressed commands use Wiki Graph URIs, not bare filesystem paths.
  Read `wikigraph help uri` before using object commands; skipping the URI rules commonly leads to invalid commands.
  Scope URIs enumerate by default and search with `--query`.
  Object URIs read one object by default.
  Do not spell `get`, `list`, or `search` as commands; the URI and `--query` select those behaviors.

Archive commands:
  wikigraph <archive-uri> create
  wikigraph <archive-uri> export
  wikigraph <archive-uri> inspect
  wikigraph transform [options]

Generation:
  wikigraph wikg://local/job add --input <chapter-uri> --task <reading-graph|reading-summary|knowledge-graph> --accept-cost
  wikigraph wikg://local/job list
  wikigraph wikg://local/job/<job-id> get|watch|pause|resume|cancel|boost|set

Maintenance:
  wikigraph <archive-uri>|<object-uri>
  wikigraph <archive-uri> set
  wikigraph <cover-uri>
  wikigraph <chapter-collection-uri> add
  wikigraph <chapter-uri>/state
  wikigraph <chapter-uri> move|remove|reset
  wikigraph <chapter-uri>/source set
  wikigraph <chapter-uri>/summary set
  wikigraph <chapter-uri>/title set
  wikigraph <archive-uri>/chapter/tree
  wikigraph <archive-uri>/chapter/tree set
  wikigraph wikg://local/config/llm get|put|set|delete|clear|test
  wikigraph wikg://local/config/concurrent get|put|set|delete|clear
  wikigraph wikg://local/config/wikispine get|put|set|delete|clear|test
